track_notes: April 2014 - they have masts in this area assessing the viability for a wind farm. At present the rough, badly drained track takes you through the wood to a ruined farmstead at Fell. Route then steepens to the summit which has good take off on VHF. Transit time for us was 56 minutes at the end of a long day...we were weary but elated to have completed our plan on our return to Fell bridge.
track_title: Poor track from Fell Bridge via ruin at Fell
